914
00:53:44.836 --> 00:53:47.462
<font color="#00ffff">Wir schauen, was der Bundesrat</font>
<font color="#00ffff">festgehalten hat.</font>

915
00:53:58.167 --> 00:54:02.884
<font color="#00ffff">Vertrauen Sie dem Bundesrat</font>
<font color="#00ffff">und ihrer Parteikollegin Sommaruga</font>

916
00:54:03.526 --> 00:54:06.153
<font color="#00ffff">so wenig,</font>
